{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSSupportsRule","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></strong> インターフェイスは、1 個の CSS <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/@supports\"><code>@supports</code></a> <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/At-rule\">@-規則</a> を表すオブジェクトを表します。これは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a> インターフェイス、さらに型定数の値が <code>12</code> (<code>CSSRule.SUPPORTS_RULE</code>) の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a> インターフェイスと <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a> インターフェイスを実装します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<p>構文は、<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/WebIDL/\" rel=\" noopener\">WebIDL</a> 形式で記述されます。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">interface CSSSupportsRule : CSSConditionRule {\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a>、さらに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a> の両方のインターフェイスを持つため、<code>CSSSupportsRule</code> は、これらのインターフェイスのプロパティも実装します。固有のプロパティはありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a>、さらに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a> の両方のインターフェイスを持つため、<code>CSSSupportsRule</code> は、これらのインターフェイスのメソッドも実装します。固有のプロパティはありません。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/#the-csssupportsrule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"ja\">CSSSupportsRule の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">勧告候補</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSSupportsRule","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/@supports\"><code>@supports</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"CSSSupportsRule インターフェイスは、1 個の CSS @supports @-規則 を表すオブジェクトを表します。これは、CSSConditionRule インターフェイス、さらに型定数の値が 12 (CSSRule.SUPPORTS_RULE) の CSSRule インターフェイスと CSSGroupingRule インターフェイスを実装します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSSupportsRule","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSSupportsRule","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/csssupportsrule","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/csssupportsrule/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule","title":"CSSSupportsRule"}],"pageTitle":"CSSSupportsRule - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}